{"tid":2165271,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國通知香港暫停移交逃犯協定、移交被判刑人士，以及豁免國際航運利得稅","createTime":"2020-08-19T17:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T21:23:46.000Z","uid":285559,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9eec5b885f4463fdda0b96376588db3c4619887","tid":2165271,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"美國國務院表示，已經通知香港當局，美方已暫停或終止與香港的三項雙邊協議，包括移交逃犯協定、移交被判刑人士，以及豁免國際航運利得稅。<br />\n<br />\n國務院發言人奧塔古斯在聲明中說，中國共產黨採取嚴厲採施，削弱根據《中英聯合聲明》向英國及香港人民承諾，賦予香港50年高度自治，美國將因而視香港為「一國一制」，並會對破壞香港人民自由的個人採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又說，華府的行動是要突顯對北京實施《國家安全法》的深切關注，認為有關法例破壞香港人民的自由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544771-20200820.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544771-20200820.htm&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRufbvH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=2fb50661\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544771-20200820.htm&h=514e6b4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544771-20200820.htm</a>"},{"pid":"05721b853ec65d2c7ab4a403ac939244cb1d5487","tid":2165271,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:20:08.000Z","msg":"正苦：香港事務屬中國内政，美方......"},{"pid":"479edd1b72e36c6351de86051906a37d1df943c0","tid":2165271,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85530e171e353606624288eebab55a117a2167b","tid":2165271,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"479edd1b72e36c6351de86051906a37d1df943c0","tid":2165271,"uid":41087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T17:21:15.000Z","msg":"逃犯天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T21:23:46.000Z","msg":"777話上帝天堂有留位俾佢 上帝果然冇吹水<img 